headline.main: BRITISH NOW FEAR A NORSE-NAZI DEAL; That Possibility Is Put Among Difficulties Facing Allies as Result of Retreat in North SWEDES EXPECTED TO BOW Submission to Reich Demands Foreseen--Berlin Held Likely to Quicken Pace of War
